data.description: **Introducing Your Dream Home nestled in the picturesque Jones Farm Neighborhood, this beautiful traditional home with meticulously landscaped grounds is a true masterpiece. Elegance, comfort, and modern convenience blend seamlessly in this remarkable residence.**A Grand Entrance** The vaulted entryway sets the tone for this exceptional home, welcoming you with its grandeur and grace. The formal dining room provides a perfect backdrop for special gatherings, overlooking the lush front yard landscaping. This is where cherished memories are made. The Living Room & Family Room boasts a cozy gas fireplace, creating a warm and inviting ambiance, ideal for relaxation and quality time. The kitchen is a chef's paradise, featuring new Samsung appliances, gas cooking, granite tile counters, glass front cabinetry with undermount lighting. The corner sink offers a scenic view of the pristine backyard, making meal preparation a delightful experience. Step into the backyard, a meticulously maintained oasis. This outdoor space is a haven of tranquility, with immaculate grounds perfect for relaxation and outdoor entertainment. Whether it's your morning coffee on the patio listening to the meditative sounds of the water feature or a barbecue with friends, this backyard is designed for your enjoyment. This stunning traditional home also features central vac, new furnace, new 50 year presidential roof, effortlessly blends timeless charm with contemporary amenities. A true rarity in a highly desirable location, this property awaits your visit. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the beauty and comfort of this exceptional home. OPEN HOUSE Saturday 12/2 12p-2p , Sunday 12/3 12p-2p [Home Energy Score = 5. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222466]
